      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/Automated_Tuning\" title=\"Automated Tuning\">Automated Tuning</a> * CLOP</b>\n</p><p><b>CLOP</b> for Noisy Black-Box Parameter Optimization, \na program used for <a href=\"/Automated_Tuning\" title=\"Automated Tuning\">parameter tuning</a>, created by <a href=\"/R%C3%A9mi_Coulom\" title=\"Rémi Coulom\">Rémi Coulom</a>. The CLOP principle, which stands for <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/confidence\">Confident</a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Local_search_%28optimization%29\">Local OPtimization</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>, is an approach to <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Local_regression\">local regression</a> that overcomes problems with very <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Statistical_noise\">noisy</a> outputs and nonnegative <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hessian_matrix\">Hessians</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> in a simple and efficient way. CLOP is suited to tune several parameters simultaneously, and requires polynomial <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Time_complexity\">time</a> for each additional parameter to verify the tuned values, that is playing a lot of games <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#See_also\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">See also</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Publications</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2011_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2011 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#2015_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2015 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#2020_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2020 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=CLOP&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: See also\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Match_Statistics\" title=\"Match Statistics\">Match Statistics</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Cutechess-cli\" title=\"Cutechess-cli\">Cutechess-cli</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/SPSA\" title=\"SPSA\">SPSA</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Publications\">Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=CLOP&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/R%C3%A9mi_Coulom\" title=\"Rémi Coulom\">Rémi Coulom</a> (<b>2011</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://remi.coulom.free.fr/CLOP/\">CLOP: Confident Local Optimization for Noisy Black-Box Parameter Tuning</a></i>. <a href=\"/Advances_in_Computer_Games_13\" title=\"Advances in Computer Games 13\">Advances in Computer Games 13</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://remi.coulom.free.fr/CLOP/CLOPSlides.pdf\">slides as pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/R%C3%A9mi_Coulom\" title=\"Rémi Coulom\">Rémi Coulom</a> (<b>2012</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007%2F978-3-642-31866-5_13\">CLOP: Confident Local Optimization for Noisy Black-Box Parameter Tuning</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://link.springer.com/book/10.1007/978-3-642-31866-5\">Advances in Computer Games</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lecture_Notes_in_Computer_Science\">LNCS</a>,  Vol. 7168, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Springer_Science%2BBusiness_Media\">Springer</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=CLOP&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2011_...\">2011 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=CLOP&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2011 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=40237\">CLOP for Noisy Black-Box Parameter Optimization</a> by <a href=\"/R%C3%A9mi_Coulom\" title=\"Rémi Coulom\">Rémi Coulom</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 01, 2011</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=40687\">To Ilari&#160;: CLOP + cutechess-cli</a> by <a href=\"/Marco_Costalba\" title=\"Marco Costalba\">Marco Costalba</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 09, 2011</li></ul>\n<p><b>2012</b> \n</p>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://computer-go.org/pipermail/computer-go/2012-January/004429.html\">Re: win rate bias and CLOP</a> by <a href=\"/Brian_Sheppard\" title=\"Brian Sheppard\">Brian Sheppard</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://computer-go.org/pipermail/computer-go/\">Computer-go Archives</a>, January 03, 2012</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=41816\">CLOP + cutechess cli</a> by <a href=\"/Engin_%C3%9Cst%C3%BCn\" title=\"Engin Üstün\">Engin Üstün</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 05, 2012&#160;» <a href=\"/Cutechess-cli\" title=\"Cutechess-cli\">Cutechess-cli</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=42202\">EXchess v6.10 released</a> by <a href=\"/Daniel_Homan\" title=\"Daniel Homan\">Daniel Homan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 29, 2012&#160;» <a href=\"/EXchess\" title=\"EXchess\">EXchess</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?p=454327\">CLOP on Stockfish</a> by <a href=\"/Gary_Linscott\" title=\"Gary Linscott\">Gary</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 10, 2012&#160;» <a href=\"/Stockfish\" title=\"Stockfish\">Stockfish</a></li></ul>\n<p><b>2013</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/fishcooking/8zN5TZfEN8w/KIZYLnO8c08J\">CLOP and Stockfish</a> by <a href=\"/Joona_Kiiski\" title=\"Joona Kiiski\">Joona Kiiski</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">FishCooking</a>, March 31, 2013&#160;» <a href=\"/Stockfish\" title=\"Stockfish\">Stockfish</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/fishcooking/y9maHKLrhQQ/68_yqILvcWYJ\">CLOP tuning</a> by <a href=\"/Marco_Costalba\" title=\"Marco Costalba\">Marco Costalba</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">FishCooking</a>, May 19, 2013</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/fishcooking/6Jis--X-L20/QcJ7XqUZ2-EJ\">CLOP tests are active</a> by <a href=\"/Gary_Linscott\" title=\"Gary Linscott\">Gary Linscott</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">FishCooking</a>, July 03, 2013</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=48847\">Question regarding CLOP and cutechess-cli</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Jacob_B%C3%B8rs_Lind&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Jacob Børs Lind (page does not exist)\">Jacob Børs Lind</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 05, 2013&#160;» <a href=\"/Cutechess-cli\" title=\"Cutechess-cli\">Cutechess-cli</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=49410\">Clop and cutechess</a> by <a href=\"/Alcides_Schulz\" title=\"Alcides Schulz\">Alcides Schulz</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 21, 2013</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/fishcooking/EczR5D1BKhU/thmLRG5uBdkJ\">CLOP tests are active (finally)</a> by <a href=\"/Gary_Linscott\" title=\"Gary Linscott\">Gary Linscott</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">FishCooking</a>, November 10, 2013</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/fishcooking/gmE5A05jWsg/4toIYFI6z80J\">CLOP overhead</a> by Lucas Braesch, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">FishCooking</a>, November 14, 2013</li></ul>\n<p><b>2014</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=51020\">needed CLOP for cluster</a> by <a href=\"/Daniel_Shawul\" title=\"Daniel Shawul\">Daniel Shawul</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 23, 2014</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=51167\">Help with CLOP</a> by Arjun Temurnikar, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 05, 2014</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/fishcooking/0uRw0Zila0M/s2siUjVzFFwJ\">Problem with CLOP and clop-cutechess-cli.py? (long post)</a> by joster, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">FishCooking</a>, May 10, 2014</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/fishcooking/WNrxeXAJ6VI/ZkCnRv4I_qEJ\">Goodbye CLOP, hello SPSA)</a> by <a href=\"/Gary_Linscott\" title=\"Gary Linscott\">Gary Linscott</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">FishCooking</a>, May 17, 2014 </li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/fishcooking/bW1l9oesAb8/-uMnp3Ky4UwJ\">Port of Coulom's CLOP algorithm to Python</a> by Kamyar, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">FishCooking</a>, December 03, 2014</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2015_...\">2015 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=CLOP&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: 2015 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=55042\">Working with CLOP</a> by <a href=\"/Robert_Pope\" title=\"Robert Pope\">Robert Pope</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 22, 2015</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=62012\">CLOP: when to stop?</a> by <a href=\"/Erin_Dame\" title=\"Erin Dame\">Erin Dame</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 07, 2016</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=67529\">CLOP in cutechess-cli debug</a> by <a href=\"/Albert_Silver\" title=\"Albert Silver\">Albert Silver</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 22, 2018&#160;» <a href=\"/Cutechess-cli\" title=\"Cutechess-cli\">Cutechess-cli</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=67646\">New CLOP settings give Leela huge tactics boost</a> by <a href=\"/Albert_Silver\" title=\"Albert Silver\">Albert Silver</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 04, 2018&#160;» <a href=\"/Leela_Chess_Zero\" title=\"Leela Chess Zero\">Leela Chess Zero</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2020_...\">2020 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=CLOP&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: 2020 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=72848\">Trying to CLOP again</a> by <a href=\"/Vivien_Clauzon\" title=\"Vivien Clauzon\">Vivien Clauzon</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 19, 2020 </li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=CLOP&amp